   what is go-pawz.mps?
   ÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄ-Ä-ùú

   go-pawz.mps is a mpe module written for use with mystic bbs software
   version 1.05 and later.

   go-pawz.mps is an animated pause prompt engine, which allows the sysop
   to configure up to 10 different animated pause prompts which will be
   selected at random for each pause prompt.

   go-pawz comes with ten different pause prompts.  however, its possible
   (and quite easy) to create your own if you do not like the pause
   prompts included.

   some features of go-pawz.mps:

        í adds animated pause prompts to mystic bbs
        í allows up to 10 different randomly selected pause prompts
        í inactivity timeout check (180 seconds)
        í support for non-ansi callers
        í reads entire pause file before displaying to keep system
          resources free/low
        í configurable pause delay for each file
        í no messy configuration file required
        í comes in source code form for customization

