   installation instructions
   ÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄ-Ä-ùú

   1) copy go-pawz.mps into your scripts directory, and compile it with
      MPLC.EXE.  (type: "mplc go-pawz")

   2) copy ANIPAUSE.* into the text file directory

   3) replace prompt 022 with the following (without quotes): "!go-pawz"
      for those confused, go into your root mystic bbs directory, type
      "langedit default.txt", find prompt 022 and replace it.

   4) re-compile language file.  for those confused, type:
      "makelang default.txt".

   bam!  you're done.  note that if you have multiple language files, you'll
   need to do steps #2 through #4 for each language file.

